<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q8_v11" title="Q8_v11" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>Registro del caso:</p>
    <p>Para preparar vasitos de salsa para acompañar ensaladas, se utiliza la siguiente mezcla por vasito:</p>
    <p>• Aceite de oliva: <m:math><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:math> onzas<br/>
• Jugo de limón: <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas</p>
    <p>Se prepararán <m:math><m:mn>220</m:mn></m:math> vasitos en total. Considere que <m:math><m:mn>1</m:mn></m:math> onza = <m:math><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:math> mL.</p>
    <p>De las siguientes cantidades totales de jugo de limón, en mL, ¿cuál es la única que coincide con la información anterior?</p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" shuffle="false" max-choices="1">
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">330 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Cada vasito usa <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón, así que para <m:math><m:mn>220</m:mn></m:math> vasitos se usan <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>220</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Luego, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>330</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por eso, 330 mL no coincide con la información.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">9900 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! El jugo de limón total es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>220</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas. Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL por onza, se obtiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>330</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. Por eso, 9 900 mL es la única cantidad que coincide con la información.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">13 200 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El total correcto de jugo de limón es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>220</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>330</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. En cambio, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>13&#160;200</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>440</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, que no coincide con las <m:math><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón requeridas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">23 100 mL<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. El total correcto de jugo de limón es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>220</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas y <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>330</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL. En cambio, <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>23&#160;100</m:mn><m:mo>÷</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>770</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> onzas, que no coincide con las <m:math><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón requeridas.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Identificar cuánto jugo de limón lleva cada vasito</strong></p>
            <p>Según el enunciado, cada vasito contiene <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas de jugo de limón.</p>
            <p>Eso equivale a:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:mrow></m:math> onzas</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Calcular las onzas totales de jugo de limón para 220 vasitos</strong></p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>220</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mfrac><m:mn>3</m:mn><m:mn>2</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>330</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>En total se necesitan 330 onzas de jugo de limón.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Convertir de onzas a mL</strong></p>
            <p>Como <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math> mL por onza, entonces:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>330</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>9&#160;900</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Por lo tanto, el total de jugo de limón es 9 900 mL.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Comparar con las alternativas</strong></p>
            <p>Opción A: 330 mL, no coincide.</p>
            <p>Opción B: 9 900 mL, sí coincide.</p>
            <p>Opción C: 13 200 mL, no coincide.</p>
            <p>Opción D: 23 100 mL, no coincide.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>La única cantidad total de jugo de limón que coincide con la información dada es <strong>9 900 mL</strong>, es decir, la <strong>alternativa B</strong>.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>